spaska.clusterers

Interface IClusterer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Parametrable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FuzzyKMeans, SimpleKMeans, ZeroClusterer

    public interface IClusterer
extends Parametrable
    An interface representing all clustering algorithms in the system. If you want to implement a custom clustering algorithm you should implement this interface.
